text.div:
Process Outcome Codes

This value set includes sample Process Outcome codes.

Copyright Statement: This is an example set.

This code system http://hl7.org/fhir/processoutcomecodes defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition
complete CompleteThe requested processing has completed.
pended PendedThe requested processing has been suspended.
error ErrorThe requested processing has terminated with some errors being found.

title: Process Outcome Codes
